Invocation Name: cruz f. m. saskatoon
des:
Listen to Saskatoon Cruz F .M.....a 70s, 80s, 90s and 2000s Classic Hits radio station in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan. Listen live and access on-demand content.
Once enabled, just say: "Alexa, open cruz f. m. saskatoon" and Alexa will guide you from there!
After that, you can say things like:
 * "Listen to on demand"
 * "Resume"
 * "On demand options"
When playing audio, you can say:
 * Alexa, pause
When playing on-demand content, you can skip to an older show by saying:
 * Alexa, next
And navigate to the previous segment by saying:
 * Alexa, go back
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
